name: Vanguard USD Treasury Bond UCITS ETF GBP Hedged Distributing
description_en: The Vanguard USD Treasury Bond UCITS ETF GBP Hedged Distributing seeks to track the Bloomberg Global Aggregate US Treasury Float Adjusted (GBP Hedged) index. The Bloomberg Global Aggregate US Treasury Float Adjusted (GBP Hedged) index tracks US sovereign debt, issued by the US government. 'Float adjusted' means, the index does not consider bonds that are unavailable to the public. Currency hedged to British Pound (GBP). The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.10% p.a.. The ETF replicates the performance of the underlying index by sampling technique (buying a selection of the most relevant index constituents). The interest income (coupons) in the ETF is distributed to the investors (Monthly). The Vanguard USD Treasury Bond UCITS ETF GBP Hedged Distributing is a very small ETF with 1m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 8 February 2022 and is domiciled in Ireland.

Měna zajišťovala britskou libru (GBP). TER (celkový poměr nákladů) ETF činí 0,10% p.a. ETF replikuje výkon základního indexu technikou vzorkování (nákup výběru nejdůležitějších složek indexu). Úrokové výnosy (kupóny) v ETF jsou distribuovány investorům (měsíčně). Hrpová distribuce Vanguard USD Treasury Bond UCITS ETF GBP je velmi malá ETF s vedením 1m euro. ETF byl spuštěn 8. února 2022 a má bydliště v Irsku.

name: HSBC Europe Screened Equity UCITS ETF EUR (Dist)
description_en: The HSBC Europe Screened Equity UCITS ETF EUR (Dist) seeks to track the FTSE Developed Europe ESG Low Carbon Select index. The FTSE Developed Europe ESG Low Carbon Select index tracks large and mid cap securities from Europe. The index aims to reduce carbon emissions and fossil fuel consumption by 50 percent each and to improve the ESG (environmental, social and governance) rating by 20 percent, compared to its parent index (FTSE Developed Europe index). Excluded sectors and companies: weapons, thermal coal, tobacco, nuclear power, non-compliance with UN Global Compact. The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.15% p.a.. The HSBC Europe Screened Equity UCITS ETF EUR (Dist) is the cheapest ETF that tracks the FTSE Developed Europe ESG Low Carbon Select index. The ETF replicates the performance of the underlying index by full replication (buying all the index constituents). The dividends in the ETF are distributed to the investors (Semi annually). The HSBC Europe Screened Equity UCITS ETF EUR (Dist) is a very small ETF with 1m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 5 July 2022 and is domiciled in Ireland.

FTSE vyvinula Europe ESG ESG Low Carbon Select Index sleduje velké a střední cap cenné papíry z Evropy. Cílem indexu je snížit emise uhlíku a spotřebu fosilních paliv o 50 procent a zlepšit hodnocení ESG (environmentální, sociální a správa věcí veřejných) o 20 procent ve srovnání s jeho mateřským indexem (FTSE vyvinul index Europe). HSBC Europe Screebed Equity UCITS ETF EUR (DIST) je velmi malý ETF s 1m euro managementu. ETF byl spuštěn 5. července 2022 a je sídlem v Irsku.
